                        <p>Gang band is a tool that allows you to create your own music with a deliberately wobbly tool. Its goal is to challenge its visitors to recreate known sounds and melodies. It is also a platform for exchange (like a blog) which allows to discuss the good reproduction of the music created on the site.<br> My job was to work on setting the <span class="colored">style</span> up.</p>
